            <h2 style="text-align: center">Carol Danvers - Founder and CEO</h2>
            <br />
            <img src="Images/YoungWomanCEO300.jpg" alt="CompanyCEO" style="float: right" />
            <p>Prior to founding HBW, Carol gained an associate's degree in web design from the Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT) and has since worked at Google and Facebook. In 2015, Carol launched HBW with the intention of providing clients a reputable partner that could help them grow their online presence. She passionately believes that the success of HBW is down to the expertise, creativity, vision and enthusiasm of the team</p>
        </div>
