            <br />
            <img src="Images/YoungBusinessMan300.jpg" alt="SeniorWebDeveloper" style="float: left" />
            <p>Nick joined in 2015 and brought with him more than 10 years of experience providing mobile applications and web development services to clients based in the UK and Europe. He holds a Bachelor's degree in computer science from the University of Warwick. Outside of work, Nick is a member of the National Rifle Association and enters competitions across the UK.</p>
